<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721上環影片/圖片集結post]屌你上環都好撚重要！！！文宣組入黎幫手推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349459</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！</span><br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"113370062b0ead1c218b2382f53d688d272770e2","tid":1343310,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef461b1f1341f7407359b642fdc467536a1b7174","tid":1343310,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:33:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警 警黑勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">議會係講未來政制方向，唔會係抗爭大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係咪連建立新秩序都無需要呀！<br />\n係咪仲要承認共產黨呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVfqg38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVfqg38.png&h=55caeed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMoCSCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMoCSCu.png&h=9d632b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3A8vtaQ